            <p>Brief description of the blog post.</p>
            <a href="https://link-to-blog.com" target="_blank">Read Blog</a>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-post">
            <h3>Blog Post Title 2</h3>
            <p>Brief description of the blog post.</p>
            <a href="https://link-to-blog.com" target="_blank">Read Blog</a>
        </div>
        <div class="blog-post">
            <h3>Blog Post Title 3</h3>
            <p>Brief description of the blog post.</p>
            <a href="https://link-to-blog.com" target="_blank">Read Blog</a>
        </div>
        <!-- Add more blogs as needed -->
    </section>
</body>
</html>
